  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/130b0817814ccbdec9d282dfa578c209.poster.avif?t=1631891131\" width=600 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/130b0817814ccbdec9d282dfa578c209.webm?t=1631891131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/130b0817814ccbdec9d282dfa578c209.mp4?t=1631891131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Street Dreams</strong></i> is a minimal, fast-paced VR shooter set in a psychedelic dream world. Choose from a variety of weapons to defend yourself from oncoming opponents, gain points, and earn yourself a position on the global leaderboard!<br><br>Inspired by works such as <i>Mad Max: Fury Road</i> and <i>Grand Theft Auto</i>, <i><strong>Street Dreams</strong></i> places you in a high-speed car chase with the goal to wreak havoc on your pursuers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/e87699cefa4ba9ccaaf7cb90e1403c68.poster.avif?t=1631891131\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/e87699cefa4ba9ccaaf7cb90e1403c68.webm?t=1631891131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711910/extras/e87699cefa4ba9ccaaf7cb90e1403c68.mp4?t=1631891131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Five</i> unique weapons to use throughout each car chase - whether you want to maximise points, maintain high accuracy, or need to get yourself out of a tight situation - the gun you need is at an arm's reach.<br></li><li> Compete for the crown - Rack up as many points as possible to score the number one spot on the leaderboards.<br></li><li> An intense, modern soundtrack to accompany your journey, from various producers and sub-genres.</li></ul>",
